nodes.text: Ed Dunkley provided video services for the Star Wars: Clone Wars television series, as well as Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within, The Mexican, Jay and Silent Bob Strike Back, 40 Days and 40 Nights, Envy, Shrek 2, Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones, and Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith. He was also a visual effects staff member for Twister, Jurassic Park, Casper, Mars Attacks!, Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace, and Wild Wild West.
